profile:
As local Comox Valley plumbing contractors located in Courtenay BC, Tyee Mechanical Plumbing & Gas is dedicated to giving its customers the best plumbing, heating, and gas services available.

We have the experience to handle a great variety of plumbing, heating and gas services and understand the need for efficiency and quality for all your installations and repairs. Emergency Plumber We understand that sometimes plumbing emergencies happen that need to be handled fast! This is why we’re pleased to offer an emergency plumber service. Our 24 hour plumbing service means that you can rest easy knowing help is only a quick phone call away. Be sure to keep our number handy and call 250-218-7688 whenever you need an emergency plumbing service. Serving Comox, Courtenay, and Cumberland, Denman Island and Hornby Island Proud to call the Comox Valley home, we offer our plumbing services to businesses and residents in Comox, Courtenay, and Cumberland, and the surrounding areas including Denman Island, Fanny Bay, Union Bay, Black Creek and Merville. Our work is guaranteed and we pride ourselves on building long lasting relationships with our customers. Whether you’re looking for help with a water heater, leak detection, toilet repair, drain cleaning, a leaky faucet, or are looking for a plumbing contractor for a residential or commercial project, we’re here to help! For more information be sure to read our plumbing reviews on our Google+ page, and be check out our Facebook page for updates and information on keeping your home safe, warm, and dry!
